This is a Region 2 DVD (as stated in the title) and will NOT play on US or Canadian DVD players.  Check out the sellers. They are all out of the country and/or importers!  This review has nothing to do with whether this DVD is good or bad...just a warning that it would be a waste of money if you live in the US or Canada.

If the editorial is correct then this cannot be Season 9, that aired world wide this year (2013).  Some discrepancies are: Wild Bill is not on the Kodiak and Elliot Neese is not on the Rambling Rose.  So which is wrong - the editorial or the DVD?  I love Deadliest Catch, but will not be spending money on this one till I know the truth!
